videos.headline: Duke's game-winning drive
videos.description: In the fourth overtime, Duke's QB Thomas Sirk lobs it up to TE Erich Schneider for a touchdown to tie the game. Duke then converts on a two-point conversion to win the game 45-43 over Virginia Tech.
